X-Men - Apocalypse Vs. Dracula (01 - 04) (2006) (FBScan)

Dracula Vs Apocalypse is a tale of Clan Akkaba the descendants of Apocalypse who become targets of Dracula for an affront Apocalypse perpetrated against him while he was still mortal. It reveals that Jonothon Starsmore and Blink of generation X are descendants of Apocalypse and sets up the background for Apocalypse 's blood being a potent mutagen and Ozymandias eventual rebellion and betrayal of Apocalypse.
